{"word":"συγκαλύπτω","slug":"συγκαλύπτω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συγκαλύπτω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ψω</el>) </el><p/><i>to cover</i> or <i>veil completely</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>: <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>συγκεκαλυμμένη</el> <i>muffled up</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>:— <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to wrap oneself up, cover one's face</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/>"}]}